[tabs layout="horizontal"]

<h1>You can also choose between "outline" and "thin outline"!</h1>

[title padding_top=0 padding_bottom=10 style=line]Thin Outline[/title]
[button color="peach" size="medium" link="#" style="thin outline"]Button[/button]Â [button color="magenta" size="medium" link="#" style="thin outline"]Button[/button] [button color="red" size="medium" link="#" style="thin outline"]Button[/button] [button color="orange" size="medium" link="#" style="thin outline"]Button[/button] [button color="yellow" size="medium" link="#" style="thin outline"]Button[/button] [button color="green" size="medium" link="#" style="thin outline"]Button[/button] [button color="sage" size="medium" link="#" style="thin outline"]Button[/button] [button color="blue" size="medium" link="#" style="thin outline"]Button[/button] [button color="navy" size="medium" link="#" style="thin outline"]Button[/button]Â [button color="purple" size="medium" link="#" style="thin outline"]Button[/button] [button color="brown" size="medium" link="#" style="thin outline"]Button[/button]Â [button color="black" size="medium" link="#" style="thin outline"]Button[/button]Â [button color="dark" size="medium" link="#" style="thin outline"]Button[/button] [button color="gray" size="medium" link="#" style="thin outline"]Button[/button]

[/one_half]

[divider height="20"]

[code]

Button Shortcode

================

&nbsp;

[button url="#" target="_blank" color="primary" size="medium" style="traditional"] Button Text [/button]

&nbsp;

Size: small, medium (default), large
Color: primary color (default), magenta, red, peach, orange, yellow, green, sage, blue, purple, brown, black, dark, gray/grey... or use a hex color code like "#00A0BF"
Target: _blank, _self
Style: traditional (default), flat, outline, thin outline

[/code]

[space count="2"]

		<content:encoded><![CDATA[[title size="1" style="plain" align="center"]Use FontAwesome icons with Toggles &amp; Accordions![/title]

[divider height="30"]
[columns]
[column size="one_half"]

[title size="3" style="line" padding_bottom="10"]Toggles (default icon)[/title]

[toggles]
[toggle title="Toggle" open="yes"]...toggle content...[/toggle]
[toggle title="Toggle" open="no"]...toggle content...[/toggle]
[toggle title="Toggle" open="no"]...toggle content...[/toggle]
[/toggles]

[/column]

[column size="one_half"]

[title size="3" style="line" padding_bottom="10"]AccordionÂ (default icon)[/title]

[accordion]
[toggle title="Toggle" open="yes"]...toggle content...[/toggle]
[toggle title="Toggle" open="no"]...toggle content...[/toggle]
[toggle title="Toggle" open="no"]...toggle content...[/toggle]
[/accordion]

[/column]
[/columns]

[/toggles]

[title size="3" style="line" padding_bottom="10"]Highlighted Text[/title]

Along came a [highlight color="yellow"]highlighted area ofÂ text[/highlight], but thenÂ [highlight color="black"]another highlighted area[/highlight] became jealous and danced his own little jig to get attention. [highlight text_color="white" background_color="primary"]Diam adipiscing magna[/highlight], sit amet tempus mi magna sed nulla. Duis quis nibh ac nisi congue feugiat a nec erat.

		<content:encoded><![CDATA[[title size="3" style="line" align="center" padding_bottom="10"]Custom Lists (using <a href="http://fortawesome.github.io/Font-Awesome/icons/">FontAwesome</a> icons!)[/title]

[center]Any FontAwesome icon can be used and colored to make your lists more appealing.[/center]

[divider height="20"]

[one_fourth last="no"]

[list type="check"]
<ul>
	<li>Item #1</li>
	<li>Item #2</li>
	<li>Item #3</li>
</ul>
[/list]

[/one_fourth]

[one_fourth last="no"]

[list type="thumbs-up"]
<ul>
	<li>Item #1</li>
	<li>Item #2</li>
	<li>Item #3</li>
</ul>
[/list]

[/one_fourth]

[one_fourth last="no"]

[list icon="thumbs-down"]
<ul>
	<li>Item #1</li>
	<li>Item #2</li>
	<li>Item #3</li>
</ul>
[/list]

[/one_fourth]

[one_fourth last="yes"]

[list type="circle"]
<ul>
	<li>Item #1</li>
	<li>Item #2</li>
	<li>Item #3</li>
</ul>
[/list]

[/one_fourth]

[divider height="40"]

[one_fourth last="no"]

[list type="flag" icon_color="primary"]
<ul>
	<li>Item #1</li>
	<li>Item #2</li>
	<li>Item #3</li>
</ul>
[/list]

[/one_fourth]

[one_fourth last="no"]

[list type="info-circle" icon_color="purple"]
<ul>
	<li>Item #1</li>
	<li>Item #2</li>
	<li>Item #3</li>
</ul>
[/list]

[/one_fourth]

[one_fourth last="no"]

[list type="check" icon_color="blue"]
<ul>
	<li>Item #1</li>
	<li>Item #2</li>
	<li>Item #3</li>
</ul>
[/list]

[/one_fourth]

[one_fourth last="yes"]

[list type="heart" icon_color="coral"]
<ul>
	<li>Item #1</li>
	<li>Item #2</li>
	<li>Item #3</li>
</ul>
[/list]

[/one_fourth]

[divider height="40"]

[title size="3" style="line" align="center" padding_bottom="20"]Standard Lists[/title]

[one_half last="no"]
<ul>
	<li>Item #1</li>
	<li>Item #2</li>
	<li>Item #3
<ul>
	<li>Item #3a</li>
	<li>Item #3b</li>
</ul>
</li>
	<li>Item #4</li>
</ul>
[/one_half]

[one_half last="yes"]
<ol>
	<li>Item #1</li>
	<li>Item #2</li>
	<li>Item #3
<ol>
	<li>Item #3a</li>
	<li>Item #3b</li>
</ol>
</li>
	<li>Item #4</li>
</ol>
[/one_half]

[divider height="40"]

[code]

List Shortcode

==============

Standard lists are created by simply using the "visual" editor in WordPress. To create a custom list, do the same, then wrap with the list shortcode as seen below...

[list icon="" icon_color=""]
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Item #1&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Item #2&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Item #3&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
[/list]

icon:Â (please see: fortawesome.github.io/Font-Awesome/icons/)

icon_color:Â (default: same as text), primary (from Theme Options), red, orange, yellow, green, coral, blue, purple, brown, black, dark, gray/grey... or use a hex color code like "#00A0BF"

[/code]

		<title>Login Required</title>
		<link>http://enpelootas.dreamhosters.com/login-required/</link>
		<pubDate>Thu, 01 Jan 2015 09:17:18 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[stevmachine]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://themestockyard.com/maddux.test/?p=418</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[Lorem ipsum eu ut iaculis massa vestibulum at, etiam donec libero nostra malesuada varius, nisl malesuada cursus rutrum est iaculis amet nullam cubilia cursus.

Velit felis netus suspendisse suscipit nec habitasse malesuada in, interdum ornare elit metus quisque aliquam placerat, metus aenean pulvinar mauris curabitur habitant fusce tellus malesuada dapibus fermentum vitae eros curabitur morbi.

Consequat vitae cursus dolor pharetra sed lectus feugiat integer etiam commodo aenean fermentum nam dui, curae consequat duis ornare luctus molestie quis facilisis sem euismod molestie pretium fames bibendum porttitor imperdiet enim sapien ullamcorper.

Sociosqu rutrum tortor sociosqu inceptos vitae est risus, lorem aliquam sit sociosqu metus ante, phasellus bibendum curabitur tristique orci sit libero cras porta viverra hac class quam non augue vitae pharetra aliquet ac elit.

Arcu diam ad posuere sed gravida pulvinar laoreet nulla, placerat neque laoreet imperdiet sociosqu at libero suscipit metus, sagittis curabitur morbi integer sodales litora senectus.]]></content:encoded>

		<title>Touring: Vineyard hopping</title>
		<link>http://enpelootas.dreamhosters.com/vineyard-hopping/</link>
		<pubDate>Sun, 03 May 2015 19:02:44 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[stevmachine]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://themestockyard.com/greyson.test/?p=37</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[[dropcap text_color="" background_color=""]L[/dropcap]orem ipsum vulputate mauris nostra praesent lobortis aliquet quis, tristique netus diam id iaculis auctor ultricies porttitor condimentum, diam ornare orci ultricies mi purus himenaeos aenean vel aenean scelerisque conubia feugiat cursus est duis, vivamus volutpat luctus malesuada curabitur duis.

Mattis aenean eget pellentesque interdum [highlight color="yellow" text_color="" background_color="" background_opacity="1.00"]amet senectus ornare, curabitur at[/highlight] viverra ligula himenaeos litora, nulla primis ut turpis erat metus aptent augue sollicitudin iaculis aptent at metus aliquam nam cubilia, mauris tellus feugiat rhoncus aenean non bibendum leo nisl, curae imperdiet suscipit leo ut fusce ac velit id eleifend lorem a adipiscing sollicitudin imperdiet sed pretium nostra posuere praesent.

[blockquote attributed_to="Ernest Hemingway" attributed_to_url="http://themeforest.net/user/themestockyard" align="left" pull="right"]Faucibus potenti praesent elementum dictum velit quam bibendum nullam varius at nec[/blockquote]

Est tellus cubilia in convallis aptent aliquet adipiscing curabitur, lectus donec lectus proin consequat malesuada felis amet ut, mollis congue dolor lobortis hac facilisis feugiat felis ut lacinia hac dui nullam risus pulvinar consequat cubilia, etiam premium WordPress themes turpis taciti vestibulum ultricies, semper sed est vitae lacinia vel auctor curae bibendum ornare metus vehicula pulvinar curabitur, elit pretium dolor eget ipsum, cras amet duis lectus.

Aliquam scelerisque elementum senectus pulvinar blandit tortor cras placerat, ad velit nibh senectus viverra mattis hendrerit, ut nec mi felis gravida et ut quam molestie ut fringilla fusce turpis proin senectus himenaeos phasellus litora, aenean a urna porttitor mollis nibh tincidunt massa.]]></content:encoded>

Mattis aenean eget pellentesque interdum [highlight color="yellow" text_color="" background_color="" background_opacity="1.00"]amet senectus ornare, curabitur at[/highlight]Â viverra ligula himenaeos litora, nulla primis ut turpis erat metus aptent augue sollicitudin iaculis aptent at metus aliquam nam cubilia, mauris tellus feugiat rhoncus aenean non bibendum leo nisl, curae imperdiet suscipit leo ut fusce ac velit id eleifend lorem a adipiscing sollicitudin imperdiet sed pretium nostra posuere praesent.

[blockquote attributed_to="Ernest Hemingway" attributed_to_url="http://themeforest.net/user/themestockyard" align="left" pull="left"]Faucibus potenti praesent elementum dictum velit quam bibendum nullam varius at nec[/blockquote]

Est tellus cubilia in convallis aptent aliquet adipiscing curabitur, lectus donec lectus proin consequat malesuada felis amet ut, mollis congue dolor lobortis hac facilisis feugiat felis ut lacinia hac dui nullam risus pulvinar consequat cubilia, etiam <a href="http://themestockyard.com">premium WordPress themes</a>Â turpis taciti vestibulum ultricies, semper sed est vitae lacinia vel auctor curae bibendum ornare metus vehicula pulvinar curabitur, elit pretium dolor eget ipsum, cras amet duis lectus.

Aliquam scelerisque elementum senectus pulvinar blandit tortor cras placerat, ad velit nibh senectus viverra mattis hendrerit, ut nec mi felis gravida et ut quam molestie ut fringilla fusce turpis proin senectus himenaeos phasellus litora, aenean a urna porttitor mollis nibh tincidunt massa.]]></content:encoded>
